'''Paan trees''' were an evergreen [[Species/Legends|species]] of [[Tree/Legends|tree]] native to the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Hapes/Legends|Hapes]]. Traded throughout the [[Hapes Consortium/Legends|Hapes Consortium]], the paan tree was used as a screen in decorative landscapes.

